text: A gubernatorial election was held on 7 April 2019 to elect the next Governor of Kanagawa. == Candidates == *Yūji Kuroiwa back by LDP, Komeito, DPFP. *Makiko Kishi, back by the JCP and SDP. The CDP decided to not supported the incumbent. == Results == http://www.pref.kanagawa.jp/docs/em7/cnt/f5/documents/01chiji.pdf == References == == External links == * Category:2019 elections in Japan Category:Gubernatorial elections in Japan Category:Politics of Kanagawa Prefecture
title: 2019 Kanagawa gubernatorial election
